query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_products,
  SUM(CASE WHEN particleSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_particle_size,
  SUM(CASE WHEN poreSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_pore_size,
  SUM(CASE WHEN columnLength IS NOT NULL AND innerDiameter IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_dimensions,
  SUM(CASE WHEN phMin IS NOT NULL AND phMax IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as has_ph_range,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN particleSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1) as particle_size_pct,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN poreSize IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1) as pore_size_pct,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN columnLength IS NOT NULL AND innerDiameter IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1) as dimensions_pct,
  ROUND(SUM(CASE WHEN phMin IS NOT NULL AND phMax IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) * 100.0 / COUNT(*), 1) as ph_range_pct
FROM products
WHERE status = 'active';
